metadata.name: Party Beast
metadata.description:
A berserk crazy beast is having fun in the party after a long day of hunting. The taste of an eye balls beer with candy colour foam is so tempting that he can't stop drinking more and more!

Each sip he sips is making him getting higher and higher and the colours around him turns to be brighter and brighter. 

Let's get drunk in this colourful world with him!
